title: When Your Data Tells You Who You Really Are
description: Spotify Wrapped is a fun look back at our year’s musical choices, good and bad. It also shows how detailed and personal data collection can be.

title: Amazon's Quest for the 'Holy Grail' of Robotics
description: Automating some warehouse functions could let the giant do more with its existing workforce—or the retailer may not require all the humans it employs today.

title: Apple Makes Plans to Move Production Out of China
description: Burned by Covid lockdowns and worker protests at Foxconn plants, the iPhone maker is looking to diversify the supply chain that has powered its growth.
